Package src.game.player

Class StoreHouse

java.lang.Object
src.game.player.StoreHouse
public class StoreHouse extends Object
A class to represent a store house of an Player, each store house has a maximum capacity of 12 elements and starts with 2 land colonists, 2 sea colonists, 1 wine good, 1 brick good, 1 tool good, 1 cloth good, and 2 food goods.
Author:
devinlinux
